## Core Use Cases

### Developer Use Cases

* Ask coding questions ("Explain this error")
* Generate code in multiple languages
* Debug compile/runtime errors
* Upload files or repositories for analysis
* Ask repo‑level questions ("Where is auth handled?")
* Run and test code safely
* Automate workflows (CI‑like tasks)
* View chat history and execution logs

### Admin Use Cases

* Manage users and roles
* Monitor executions and resource usage
* View system and security logs
* Configure AI, execution, and system limits

